With the move to International Financial Reporting Standards (IFRS) for many of the world’s public companies has become a lot more complicated. As business becomes more global, with new markets opening up seemingly every day, a company’s financial accounting must meet global standards.

Our Capital Markets group provides support at every stage of the listing process.
